
div.container-fluid#wrapper
  div.row.clearfix#top
    div.col-md-12.column#slide
  h1.text-center#tagline Your Brand. Your Vision.
  div.row.clearfix#copyText
    div.col-md-1
    div.col-md-10
      p.text-center
        | We are <b>The Store Decor Company!</b> <br><span id="smallFont">Focused on fulfilling your vision for that "extraordinary customer experience".
        | <br>Our experienced team understands the challenges you face in a competitive sales environment. We promise to integrate our knowledge and ability into your brand communication strategy to maximize your profitability goals.
        | <br>We specialize in the conquering the impossible! Here's just some of what we can do:</span>
    div.col-md-1
  div.row.clearfix#middle
    div.col-md-1
    div.col-md-10
      div.row.clearfix
        div.col-md-4#sections
          div.row.clearfix#rowCapa
            h1.text-center.sectionText Capabilities
          div.row.clearfix#rowServ
            h1.text-center.sectionText Services
          div.row.clearfix#rowProd
            h1.text-center.sectionText Products
        div.col-md-8#sectionInfo
